column5:
Lost in making decisions, some alternate reality. Exhausted by the beautiful things that could be true and still can be happening. I just need a way out, of my head. All the things I do and spend a little time in hell. They told me; it only gets better. 
And I do anything for a way out. Of my head. 
All the daydreaming how my life can be but not is.
I put a toothpick in my nose until I sneeze, like a 10 times.
